Exception\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : DirectoryExist,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.NewItemCommand\r\n \r\nmkdir : ����ָ������ C:\\Users\\Administrator\\proactivity\\memory �����Ѵ��ڡ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ mkdir -p ~/self-improving/projects,~/self-improving/domains,~/self-im ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ResourceExists: (C:\\Users\\Admini...activity\\memory:String) [New-Item], IOException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : DirectoryExist,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.NewItemCommand\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":232,"aggregated":"mkdir : ����ָ������ C:\\Users\\Administrator\\self-improving\\projects �����Ѵ��ڡ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ mkdir -p ~/self-improving/projects,~/self-improving/domains,~/self-im ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ResourceExists: (C:\\Users\\Admini...roving\\projects:String) [New-Item], IOException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : DirectoryExist,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.NewItemCommand\r\n \r\nmkdir : ����ָ������ C:\\Users\\Administrator\\self-improving\\domains �����Ѵ��ڡ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ mkdir -p ~/self-improving/projects,~/self-improving/domains,~/self-im ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ResourceExists: (C:\\Users\\Admini...proving\\domains:String) [New-Item], IOException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : DirectoryExist,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.NewItemCommand\r\n \r\nmkdir : ����ָ������ C:\\Users\\Administrator\\self-improving\\archive �����Ѵ��ڡ�\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ mkdir -p ~/self-improving/projects,~/self-improving/domains,~/self-im ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ResourceExists: (C:\\Users\\Admini...proving\\archive:String) [N