{"type":"message","id":"99a6c85a","parentId":"0429effa","timestamp":"2026-03-16T17:01:18.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **设置完成！**\n\n## 已创建的目录结构\n\n### Self-Improving (`~/self-improving/`)\n```\n├── memory.md              # HOT 层：常用规则和偏好\n├── corrections.md         # 修正日志\n├── index.md               # 索引\n├── heartbeat-state.md     # 心跳状态\n├── projects/              # 项目特定学习\n├── domains/               # 领域特定学习\n└── archive/               # 归档\n```\n\n### Proactivity (`~/proactivity/`)\n```\n├── memory.md              # 激活偏好和边界\n├── session-state.md       # 当前任务状态\n├── heartbeat.md           # 心跳检查项\n├── patterns.md            # 可复用的主动行为\n├── log.md                 # 行动日志\n├── domains/               # 领域覆盖\n└── memory/\n    └── working-buffer.md  # 工作缓冲区\n```\n\n## 已更新的工作区文件\n- ✅ `AGENTS.md` - 添加了 Self-Improving 和 Proactivity 的路由\n- ✅ `SOUL.md` - 添加了核心行为指导\n- ✅ `HEARTBEAT.md` - 添加了心跳检查\n- ✅ `TOOLS.md` - 添加了主动工具使用指导\n\n---\n\n现在我可以：\n- 🧠 从错误中学习并改进\n- ⚡ 预判需求并主动推进工作\n- 🔄 在心跳时检查待办事项和阻塞\n\n有什么想测试或调整的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":333,"output":308,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30081,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773680469235}}
